cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.IT 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with spectrum sensing and cognitive radios, which are related to wireless networking. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes reinforcement learning algorithms for channel selection. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is relevant as the paper analyzes the security of the proposed algorithms and proposes mitigation techniques against belief manipulation attacks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with designing a sensing policy to maximize throughput while avoiding interference, which is related to control systems. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with maximizing throughput while avoiding interference, which is related to information theory.
